d the new members to reach SECONDARY state. Let me trace back through the session history to figure out when exactly \"All new members reached SECONDARY state\" appeared and what was different about that attempt. forward: I need to check the current RS status and identify which pod is primary, then scale up to 5 replicas and add the new pods to the replica set. The key concern is whether the PVCs for pods 3 and 4 still exist with potentially corrupted data, so I should verify the PVC state first before proceeding with the scaling.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1409,"cache_read_input_tokens":55609,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1409},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"367501ed-e4a5-4000-b239-5419541c94df","uuid":"d8b9a0f2-872e-438e-b7de-5da1d32a20df","request_id":"req_011CcP894moDxv21sbvbScNb"}
